{"sn22.159:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 22.159 ","sn22.159:0.2":"15. Ditthivagga ","sn22.159:0.3":"Anandasutta ","sn22.159:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn22.159:1.2":"Atha kho ayasma anando yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva …pe… bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn22.159:1.3":"“sadhu me, bhante, bhagava sankhittena dhammam desetu, yamaham bhagavato dhammam sutva eko vupakattho appamatto atapi pahitatto vihareyyan”ti. ","sn22.159:2.1":"“Tam kim mannasi, ananda, ","sn22.159:2.2":"rupam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn22.159:2.3":"“Aniccam, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.4":"“Yam pananiccam dukkham va tam sukham va”ti? ","sn22.159:2.5":"“Dukkham, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.6":"“Yam pananiccam dukkham viparinamadhammam, kallam nu tam samanupassitum: ","sn22.159:2.7":"‘etam mama, esohamasmi, eso me atta’”ti? ","sn22.159:2.8":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.9":"“Vedana … ","sn22.159:2.10":"sanna … ","sn22.159:2.11":"sankhara … ","sn22.159:2.12":"vinnanam niccam va aniccam va”ti? ","sn22.159:2.13":"“Aniccam, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.14":"“Yam pananiccam dukkham va tam sukham va”ti? ","sn22.159:2.15":"“Dukkham, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.16":"“Yam pananiccam dukkham viparinamadhammam, kallam nu tam samanupassitum: ","sn22.159:2.17":"‘etam mama, esohamasmi, eso me atta’”ti? ","sn22.159:2.18":"“No hetam, bhante”. ","sn22.159:2.19":"“Evam passam …pe… ","sn22.159:2.20":"naparam itthattayati pajanati”ti. ","sn22.159:2.21":"Dasamam. ","sn22.159:2.22":"Ditthivaggo pancamo. ","sn22.159:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","sn22.159:3.1":"Ajjhattikam etammama, ","sn22.159:3.2":"Soatta nocamesiya; ","sn22.159:3.3":"Micchasakkayattanu dve, ","sn22.159:3.4":"Abhinivesa anandenati. ","sn22.159:3.5":"Uparipannasako samatto. ","sn22.159:4.0":"Tassa uparipannasakassa vagguddanam ","sn22.159:4.1":"Anto dhammakathika vijja, ","sn22.159:4.2":"kukkulam ditthipancamam; ","sn22.159:4.3":"Tatiyo pannasako vutto, ","sn22.159:4.4":"nipatoti pavuccatiti. ","sn22.159:4.5":"Khandhasamyuttam samattam. "}